who deserves to be spoiled.

1138
00:33:10,470 --> 00:33:10,710
Yeah.

1139
00:33:19,710 --> 00:33:20,800
Hello.

1140
00:33:20,800 --> 00:33:21,880
That's so sweet.

1141
00:33:22,160 --> 00:33:22,950
Hello.

1142
00:33:23,280 --> 00:33:24,040
How is it?

1143
00:33:24,040 --> 00:33:25,230
Where did you go?

1144
00:33:25,230 --> 00:33:27,070
We went to Atlantis.

1145
00:33:27,070 --> 00:33:27,950
The water park?

1146
00:33:27,950 --> 00:33:28,560
Yeah.

1147
00:33:28,560 --> 00:33:30,280
We visited the aquarium.

1148
00:33:30,760 --> 00:33:32,310
Already holding hands?

1149
00:33:34,800 --> 00:33:36,520
I need to stick close to you guys.

1150
00:33:38,520 --> 00:33:39,590
Any confessions today?

1151
00:33:39,710 --> 00:33:40,710
Didn't he confess yesterday?

1152
00:33:41,040 --> 00:33:41,950
Who confesses every day?

1153
00:33:41,950 --> 00:33:42,590
Daily confession.

1154
00:33:42,590 --> 00:33:43,590
Confessing daily.

1155
00:33:44,070 --> 00:33:45,920
From now on, one confession a day.

1156
00:33:46,350 --> 00:33:48,190
So you'll say something sweet every day?

1157
00:33:48,190 --> 00:33:48,640
Yes.

1158
00:33:48,640 --> 00:33:49,160
Of course.

1159
00:33:49,160 --> 00:33:49,830
Yes.

1160
00:33:49,830 --> 00:33:50,760
Girls need that kind of affection.

1161
00:33:50,760 --> 00:33:51,520
Yeah, we do.

1162
00:33:51,520 --> 00:33:52,800
Say "I love you" every day.

1163
00:33:53,190 --> 00:33:54,310
Yang has changed.

1164
00:33:54,310 --> 00:33:55,950
Yang is so adorable.

1165
00:33:55,950 --> 00:33:58,190
Yang was the big sister confidante
a few days ago.

1166
00:33:58,190 --> 00:33:59,160
Now she's become...

1167
00:34:00,100 --> 00:34:01,820
(Little girl)

1168
00:34:02,700 --> 00:34:03,380
(Shy)

1169
00:34:06,190 --> 00:34:06,760
How do you feel?

1170
00:34:06,760 --> 00:34:07,760
How does it feel?

1171
00:34:07,760 --> 00:34:08,760
It's really fun.

1172
00:34:09,320 --> 00:34:10,080
Are you happy?

1173
00:34:10,080 --> 00:34:10,630
Yes, happy.

1174
00:34:10,630 --> 00:34:11,670
Mainly because of him?

1175
00:34:11,670 --> 00:34:12,150
Right.

1176
00:34:12,500 --> 00:34:14,300
(Why did I even ask?)

1177
00:34:14,600 --> 00:34:16,430
Hello.

1178
00:34:16,430 --> 00:34:17,520
I brought gifts for you all.

1179
00:34:17,520 --> 00:34:17,950
Really?

1180
00:34:17,950 --> 00:34:18,800
I want to take a look.

1181
00:34:21,040 --> 00:34:22,280
Seashells.

1182
00:34:22,280 --> 00:34:24,520
We picked different stones at the beach.

1183
00:34:24,520 --> 00:34:26,390
Each one stands for a person.

1184
00:34:26,390 --> 00:34:28,000
You could say what each stone means.

1185
00:34:28,000 --> 00:34:28,800
Then I'll (guess).

1186
00:34:28,950 --> 00:34:30,150
Which one do you think looks like...?

1187
00:34:30,150 --> 00:34:31,000
Looks like me?

1188
00:34:31,000 --> 00:34:31,360
Yeah.

1189
00:34:32,710 --> 00:34:33,630
Come on, explain.

1190
00:34:33,630 --> 00:34:34,150
Let me guess.

1191
00:34:34,150 --> 00:34:35,150
I'll guess first.

1192
00:34:35,360 --> 00:34:36,910
I like this one.

1193
00:34:36,910 --> 00:34:37,470
Not you.

1194
00:34:37,470 --> 00:34:38,150
That's not me?

1195
00:34:38,150 --> 00:34:38,600
Wait, she'll guess.

1196
00:34:38,600 --> 00:34:39,910
Then I guess it's this one.

1197
00:34:39,910 --> 00:34:40,560
Not you.

1198
00:34:40,560 --> 00:34:41,390
That's not me either?

1199
00:34:41,390 --> 00:34:42,360
Then I guess this one.

1200
00:34:42,360 --> 00:34:43,100
Not you.

1201
00:34:43,100 --> 00:34:43,470
(Complete failure)

1202
00:34:43,470 --> 00:34:43,630
This one.

1203
00:34:43,630 --> 00:34:44,710
Why this one?

1204
00:34:44,710 --> 00:34:46,600
Because it's so clean.

1205
00:34:46,620 --> 00:34:47,840
(Touched)

1206
00:34:47,840 --> 00:34:49,190
Thank you.

1207
00:34:49,190 --> 00:34:50,360
I'm about to cry.

1208
00:34:50,360 --> 00:34:51,080
Don't cry.

1209
00:34:51,080 --> 00:34:52,190
This one's the cleanest.

1210
00:34:54,080 --> 00:34:55,000
Let me pick one.

1211
00:34:55,120 --> 00:34:56,120
Guess which one is you.

1212
00:34:56,320 --> 00:34:57,360
I like this one.

1213
00:34:57,360 --> 00:34:58,520
That's you, Wan.

1214
00:34:58,520 --> 00:34:59,600
(Impressive)
Really?

1215
00:34:59,600 --> 00:34:59,950
Yeah.

1216
00:35:01,320 --> 00:35:02,320
See? It's passionate.

1217
00:35:02,320 --> 00:35:03,760
(Passionate and resolute)
And it's resolute.

1218
00:35:04,300 --> 00:35:05,620
(Love it)

1219
00:35:05,670 --> 00:35:06,670
So which one's me?

1220
00:35:06,670 --> 00:35:07,630
Take a guess.

1221
00:35:07,630 --> 00:35:08,320
Me.

1222
00:35:09,710 --> 00:35:10,520
Guess which one it is.

1223
00:35:10,520 --> 00:35:11,000
This one.

1224
00:35:11,000 --> 00:35:11,430
Yeah.

1225
00:35:11,430 --> 00:35:12,360
Why's that?

1226
00:35:12,360 --> 00:35:14,430
Because it has an amber-like glow.

1227
00:35:14,600 --> 00:35:15,360
You guess about the villager chief.

1228
00:35:17,000 --> 00:35:18,360
I'm your mountain.

1229
00:35:18,360 --> 00:35:18,840
Yeah.

1230
00:35:19,560 --> 00:35:20,120
Wow!

1231
00:35:20,360 --> 00:35:21,520
You're pretty impressive, too.

1232
00:35:21,710 --> 00:35:22,760
And then there's you and Yan.

1233
00:35:22,760 --> 00:35:24,150
Help Yan pick hers, okay?

1234
00:35:25,150 --> 00:35:26,360
Yan's is obvious.

1235
00:35:26,360 --> 00:35:27,080
This one's Yan's.

1236
00:35:27,080 --> 00:35:27,910
Yeah, totally obvious.

1237
00:35:27,910 --> 00:35:28,760
Pink.

1238
00:35:28,760 --> 00:35:29,190
Yeah.

1239
00:35:29,760 --> 00:35:31,000
Okay, guess which one is yours.

1240
00:35:31,000 --> 00:35:32,390
I think...

1241
00:35:33,230 --> 00:35:34,470
I think this one's mine.

1242
00:35:34,560 --> 00:35:35,080
You...

1243
00:35:35,080 --> 00:35:36,000
Is this him?

1244
00:35:36,120 --> 00:35:37,120
Forget if this is him?

1245
00:35:37,120 --> 00:35:37,870
(Bestie, don't crack me up)
Seems not.

1246
00:35:37,870 --> 00:35:38,470
Not this one.

1247
00:35:38,630 --> 00:35:39,560
This one's mine.

1248
00:35:40,190 --> 00:35:40,670
You...

1249
00:35:40,670 --> 00:35:41,360
You're not this either.

1250
00:35:41,360 --> 00:35:42,080
You're not this one.

1251
00:35:42,080 --> 00:35:42,840
Then I'm this one.

1252
00:35:42,840 --> 00:35:43,470
Yeah, that's you.

1253
00:35:43,470 --> 00:35:44,430
What is this?

1254
00:35:44,430 --> 00:35:44,910
Why?

1255
00:35:44,910 --> 00:35:45,840
Do I look like it?

1256
00:35:45,900 --> 00:35:47,360
(Another joke)

1257
00:35:47,360 --> 00:35:48,320
This one's cute.

1258
00:35:48,320 --> 00:35:49,150
This one's pure.

1259
00:35:49,800 --> 00:35:50,040
No.

1260
00:35:50,040 --> 00:35:50,560
(Forced retrieval)
This isn't yours.

1261
00:35:50,560 --> 00:35:50,910
Give it back.

1262
00:35:50,910 --> 00:35:52,150
Got it wrong.

1263
00:35:52,150 --> 00:35:52,760
This one's yours.

1264
00:35:52,760 --> 00:35:53,600
So neat and clean.

1265
00:35:53,600 --> 00:35:53,910
Right?

1266
00:35:53,910 --> 00:35:55,470
(I love this)
I want to say this one should be me.

1267
00:35:55,470 --> 00:35:56,360
And this is you two.

1268
00:35:56,600 --> 00:35:57,360
That's adorable.

1269
00:35:57,360 --> 00:35:58,000
The cutest one of all.

1270
00:35:58,000 --> 00:35:58,870
Is this mine?

1271
00:35:58,870 --> 00:35:59,760
Yeah.

1272
00:35:59,760 --> 00:36:00,390
This one's yours.

1273
00:36:00,390 --> 00:36:02,120
So what does mine mean?

1274
00:36:02,120 --> 00:36:04,120
There's an empty space in the middle.

1275
00:36:04,120 --> 00:36:05,520
That means you're tolerant.

1276
00:36:05,520 --> 00:36:07,710
(Tolerant)
You care a lot about everyone.

1277
00:36:07,710 --> 00:36:08,190
You're very understanding.

1278
00:36:08,190 --> 00:36:09,520
(Loving)
So you're kind of introverted.

1279
00:36:09,520 --> 00:36:10,600
(Reserved)
And it's a couple of sets.

1280
00:36:10,660 --> 00:36:11,740
(Thoughtful)

1281
00:36:12,800 --> 00:36:13,950
Yan,

1282
00:36:13,950 --> 00:36:14,840
have you had dinner yet?

1283
00:36:14,840 --> 00:36:16,190
Yeah, I have.

1284
00:36:16,380 --> 00:36:17,780
(Come on)

1285
00:36:19,000 --> 00:36:20,390
These are the stones they brought you.

1286
00:36:21,000 --> 00:36:21,600
What's this?

1287
00:36:21,800 --> 00:36:23,150
We picked them at the beach.

1288
00:36:24,520 --> 00:36:25,710
I like red.

1289
00:36:27,120 --> 00:36:28,670
(Suddenly called out)
Villager chief, what are you doing?

1290
00:36:28,910 --> 00:36:29,520
What are you doing?

1291
00:36:29,520 --> 00:36:30,670
What are you tearing apart?

1292
00:36:30,740 --> 00:36:31,710
(All seen clearly)

1293
00:36:31,710 --> 00:36:33,000
Stop breaking it apart.

1294
00:36:33,320 --> 00:36:34,000
I'll keep breaking it.

1295
00:36:34,280 --> 00:36:36,150
You're breaking apart
your own authority.

1296
00:36:36,150 --> 00:36:38,560
He feels his responsibilities
are too heavy.

1297
00:36:38,800 --> 00:36:40,120
Too many duties.

1298
00:36:40,120 --> 00:36:41,000
Never left the island.

1299
00:36:41,000 --> 00:36:42,120
Here we go again.

1300
00:36:42,120 --> 00:36:43,950
I have to stay on this island
until the last day.

1301
00:36:43,950 --> 00:36:45,760
Escort all of you to successful matches.

1302
00:36:45,760 --> 00:36:46,910
Then I'll see you on the plane.

1303
00:36:48,120 --> 00:36:48,950
Take us to the airport?

1304
00:36:48,950 --> 00:36:49,800
Yeah.

1305
00:36:49,800 --> 00:36:50,320
And then,

1306
00:36:50,320 --> 00:36:51,190
I'll just wait here.

1307
00:36:51,190 --> 00:36:52,950
When newcomers come next season,

1308
00:36:52,950 --> 00:36:54,560
I'll hand over authority.

1309
00:36:54,560 --> 00:36:56,080
Then I can leave Hainan Island.

1310
00:36:56,190 --> 00:36:57,600
You really suit Hainan Island.

1311
00:36:57,660 --> 00:36:59,620
(That hurts)

1312
00:36:59,710 --> 00:37:00,600
Grab some fruit to eat.

1313
00:37:00,600 --> 00:37:01,230
Okay, eat.

1314
00:37:01,230 --> 00:37:01,760
Let's get some fruit.

1315
00:37:02,390 --> 00:37:03,670
So sweet.

1316
00:37:04,710 --> 00:37:06,950
I'm your matchmaker shipper.

1317
00:37:07,150 --> 00:37:07,910
No, I am.

1318
00:37:07,910 --> 00:37:09,150
We both are.

1319
00:37:09,320 --> 00:37:10,320
Let me think of a name.

1320
00:37:10,950 --> 00:37:11,630
This afternoon,

1321
00:37:11,630 --> 00:37:12,800
a good friend came up with one.

1322
00:37:12,800 --> 00:37:13,600
What's the name?

1323
00:37:13,600 --> 00:37:15,080
Shaun the Sheep,
with their names' pronunciations.

1324
00:37:17,520 --> 00:37:18,630
Nice one.

1325
00:37:18,630 --> 00:37:19,560
Why Shaun?

1326
00:37:19,560 --> 00:37:20,280
Where did Shaun come from?

1327
00:37:20,280 --> 00:37:21,280
Sounds like "En" of Zhao Enda.

1328
00:37:22,000 --> 00:37:23,190
Exactly.

1329
00:37:23,190 --> 00:37:25,120
So cute.

1330
00:37:25,560 --> 00:37:26,520
You two are too sweet.

1331
00:37:26,520 --> 00:37:27,390
Honestly.

1332
00:37:27,390 --> 00:37:28,520
Nice pick.

1333
00:37:31,220 --> 00:37:48,180
("Live and Love" Release Schedule)

1334
00:37:48,470 --> 00:37:50,470
(Every Thurs. at 12 pm.)
Hi everyone, I'm actor Wang Kaimu.

1335
00:37:50,470 --> 00:37:51,880
(Watch Live and Love with us)
I'm actor Wang Gege.

1336
00:37:51,880 --> 00:37:54,270
(A little excited)
First time seeing others pair up.

1337
00:37:54,270 --> 00:37:56,030
Looking forward to them
in Live and Love.

1338
00:37:56,600 --> 00:37:57,400
Feeling secretly thrilled.

1339
00:37:57,400 --> 00:37:58,550
He's secretly thrilled.

1340
00:37:58,550 --> 00:38:00,080
I take back what I just said.

1341
00:38:00,080 --> 00:38:01,310
(Retracting my comment)
These shots make me feel...

1342
00:38:01,310 --> 00:38:02,120
she seems...

1343
00:38:02,120 --> 00:38:03,160
Handsome guy, beautiful girl.

1344
00:38:03,160 --> 00:38:04,550
(Can't help shipping)
Very pleasing to the eye.

1345
00:38:04,550 --> 00:38:06,440
You seriously don't remember
Huang Jiawei at all?

1346
00:38:07,310 --> 00:38:09,550
(Why bring that up?)
When you ship others, just ship properly.

1347
00:38:10,030 --> 00:38:12,360
(Hold on)
Feels like I'm watching a drama.

1348
00:38:12,420 --> 00:38:13,900
(Brilliant)

1349
00:38:13,990 --> 00:38:15,880
(Treating the villager chief as an NPC)
He's part of their game.

1350
00:38:16,230 --> 00:38:18,200
He purposely opened it
in front of the villager chief.

1351
00:38:18,200 --> 00:38:18,680
Those two

1352
00:38:18,680 --> 00:38:19,880
(Is this okay?)
are standing right above someone's head.

1353
00:38:19,880 --> 00:38:21,300
Stop talking, or he'll start crying.

1354
00:38:21,300 --> 00:38:21,980
(Not upset at all)

1355
00:38:22,030 --> 00:38:23,950
I can't wait to see what happens next.

1356
00:38:23,950 --> 00:38:25,270
(Urgent)
Scratching my head in impatience.

1357
00:38:25,270 --> 00:38:27,550
Really wish someone would
come disrupt their relationship.
